    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0002",
      "text": " 79",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0003",
      "text": "list maintained by each port for each specified format is vendor specific.  If the established registra-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        540.0,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0004",
      "text": "tion list is full when an add registration function occurs, the port does not accept this registration, and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.87,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0005",
      "text": "rejects this request indicating \"unable to perform command request\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        398.65,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0006",
      "text": "A Logout occurring between a node and a valid-registered-recipient node shall cause de-registration",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        540.03,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0007",
      "text": "of the valid-recipient port in the established registration list maintained by the port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        457.56,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0008",
      "text": "4.2.25.3  Responsibilities of Valid-Registered Recipients",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        361.48,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0009",
      "text": "A valid-registered recipient shall be capable of receiving and processing Link Incident Records that",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        539.91,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0010",
      "text": "are generated according to the Link Incident reporting procedure (see 4.2.24.2).  The usage and co-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.05,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0011",
      "text": "ordination of Link Incident Records by ULPs is beyond the scope of this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        456.04,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0012",
      "text": "If a valid registered recipient receives a Link Incident Record for a format that does not match its reg-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.06,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0013",
      "text": "istration format, the recipient port shall reject the RLIR ELS with a reason code of \"Unable to perform",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        539.91,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0014",
      "text": "command request\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        182.31,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0015",
      "text": "4.2.25.4  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        178.22,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0016",
      "text": "a) LIRR Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        286.96,
        232.94,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p098_s0017",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        310.96,
        287.89,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
